# SwiftUI Toolbar Features

Guidelines for implementing modern toolbar features in SwiftUI.

---

## üéØ CUSTOMIZABLE TOOLBARS

### Creating a Customizable Toolbar

```swift
ContentView()
    .toolbar(id: "main-toolbar") {
        ToolbarItem(id: "tag") {
            TagButton()
        }
        ToolbarItem(id: "share") {
            ShareButton()
        }
        ToolbarSpacer(.fixed)
        ToolbarItem(id: "more") {
            MoreButton()
        }
    }
```

### Toolbar Spacers

```swift
ToolbarSpacer(.fixed)     // Fixed-width space
ToolbarSpacer(.flexible)  // Flexible space that pushes items apart
```

