## üì± PLATFORM CONSIDERATIONS

### iOS/iPadOS
- Bottom bar placement useful on iPhones
- `.searchToolbarBehavior(.minimize)` for space efficiency

### macOS
- Customizable toolbars expected in productivity apps
- Use spacers for logical groupings

